          		SECOND CALL FOR PAPERS
		Data & Knowledge Engineering Journal - Elsevier
                        Special Issue on 
  Contribution of Ontologies in Designing Advanced Information Systems
                Guest Editors:

         Ladjel Bellatreche, Guy Pierra, Yamine Ait Ameur
