SUBMISSIONS OF PAPERS 
---------------------

Authors are invited to submit original papers directly to Ladjel Bellatreche: 
bellatreche@ensma.fr

Submissions length should not exceed 20 pages and must adhere to the manuscript style of the journal:
http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/journaldescription.cws_home/505608/description#description
Acceptance will be based on relevance, technical soundness, originality, and clarity of presentation. For further information on submission, please contact the guest editors. 
Do not use online submission system of the DKE journal.

